 X(n) := \int^\pi_{-\pi} e^{inx} dB(\pi + x)
X(n), n\in \mathbb Z
\langle B \rangle(x) = x
 X(n) = e^{-in\pi}\int_{0}^{2\pi} e^{inx} dB(x) = e^{-in\pi}\left(\int_{0}^{2\pi}  \cos(nx) dB(x) + i \int_{0}^{2\pi} \sin(nx) dB(x) \right)
 \int_{0}^{2\pi} \sin(nx)\cos(nx) dx = \pi + \frac{\sin^2(2\pi n)}{2n} 
